<subSubSection id="5409358820F9A7C779F254B8F52CA916" pageId="0" pageNumber="143" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="786A5DECBA930316CB4ECC9C32F0C7E6" pageId="0" pageNumber="143">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="51DDCD98F81B023D8FB4267DA56B555E" pageId="0" pageNumber="143">
The new species is named after Dr. Virgilio Galvis 
<normalizedToken id="4A87067E6E0F2EE4CC707A4FFDDF75EC" originalValue="Ramírez">Ramirez</normalizedToken>
